This is the README file for Devel::Hints, a module providing functions
to access and manipulate compile-time hints at runtime.

* Installation

Devel::Hints uses the standard perl module install process:

    cpansign -v         # optional; see SIGNATURE for details
    perl Makefile.PL
    make                # or 'nmake' on Win32
    make test
    make install

